column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_u, p.dered_g - p.dered_r as color, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger   FROM galaxy as p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=# AND (s.z < .# AND s.z > .#)
